These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, juice
There 3 different types of food: potato, pear, onion
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, card-games, dancing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, musician, librarian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, salsa, house
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, indonesian, russian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, golf, climbing
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is the indonesian##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is the librarian##1
 3. the person drinking juice is between the russian and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the indian##1
 5. the musician is the person eating onion##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is the indian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 8. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the musician##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea    | juice   | sprite           |
| Food          | pear       | onion    | potato         |
| Hobby         | card-games    | dancing  | gardening        |
| Job           | dressmaker | musician   | librarian      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa        | house    | classical       |
| Nationality   | indonesian     | indian  | russian       |
| Sport         | rowing     | golf | climbing |

