.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: peas, garlic, pepper
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, western, spy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, salsa, techno
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, american, russian
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, cat, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, volleyball, ice-hockey
 1. the owner of the turtle is the american##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 5. the russian is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking cola is the fan of disco##1
 7. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person eating peas is the person watching musical movies##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the fan of techno##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | mirinda    | cola         |
| Food          | peas    | garlic | pepper          |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | spy  | western     |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | salsa      | disco         |
| Nationality   | russian      | american   | brazilian    |
| Pet           | goldfish        | turtle      | cat         |
| Sport         | volleyball | cricket  | ice-hockey |

