There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, australian
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, soccer, parkour
 1. the person eating artichoke is the owner of the goat##1
 2. the australian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is the person eating pear##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the brazilian and the fan of house##2
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 9. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
10. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
11. the brazilian is the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
