 6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 7. the fan of house is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the librarian is the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is between the librarian and the photographer##2
10. the american is on the left of the italian##1

