.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: pear, lemon, cranberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, entrepreneur, pilot
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, techno, electronic
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla, hamster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, sailing, badminton
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, car, motorbike
 1. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person driving the van is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is sailing and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is surfing and the owner of the hamster##2
 7. the person driving the van is between the person eating cranberry and the person drinking mirinda##2
 8. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 9. the entrepreneur is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
10. the social-worker is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | mirinda          | iced-tea         | tea      |
| Food          | pear     | lemon         | cranberry |
| Job           | pilot | entrepreneur    | social-worker   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa        | electronic          | techno        |
| Pet           | hamster        | chinchilla         | guinea-pig      |
| Sport         | sailing     | badminton | surfing   |
| Transport     | car    | van          | motorbike       |

