11. the person driving the scooter is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | juice | soy-milk      | coffee      |
| Hobby         | fishing     | baking     | puzzles  |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | comedy  | action |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | japanese     | french |
| Pet           | snake        | pony | lizard     |
| Sport         | snowboarding    | basketball | parkour   |
| Transport     | skateboard        | bike        | scooter   |

