.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, potato, asparagus
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, drawing, traveling
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, librarian, lawyer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, iced-teasy, satire
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball, golf
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person eating potato is on the left of the journalist##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person watching superhero movies and the librarian##2
5. the person eating asparagus is between the lawyer and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person watching iced-teasy movies is on the left of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | cola      | almond-milk       |
| Food          | potato      | asparagus    | pomegranate   |
| Hobby         | traveling    | reading     | drawing     |
| Job           | librarian    | journalist | lawyer   |
| Movie-Genre   | iced-teasy    | satire    | superhero       |
| Sport         | golf | rowing      | volleyball    |
| Transport     | snowmobile       | train | taxi |

