.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, water
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, corn, pineapple
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, camping, rock-climbing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, epic, family
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, salsa, r&b
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, biathlon, cycling
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat, subway
1. the person driving the boat is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person eating corn is between the person drinking water and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
8. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching family movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | water       | almond-milk     | sprite         |
| Food          | pomegranate     | corn      | pineapple     |
| Hobby         | camping | rock-climbing    | singing      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | epic | family    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa        | r&b     | punk   |
| Sport         | rugby     | biathlon | cycling |
| Transport     | boat     | subway       | quad-bike    |

