.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, cola
There 3 different types of food: orange, radish, pineapple
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, security-guard, accountant
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, colombian, pakistani
3 different pets are kept: cat, horse, chinchilla
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, snowboarding, parkour
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, scooter
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the police-officer is between the person drinking cola and the owner of the chinchilla##2
4. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the security-guard is the person eating orange##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
9. the colombian is between the person eating orange and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea    | almond-milk       | cola      |
| Food          | orange   | pineapple   | radish  |
| Job           | security-guard  | police-officer | accountant    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | colombian     | pakistani  |
| Pet           | chinchilla     | cat        | horse |
| Sport         | snowboarding | handball   | parkour  |
| Transport     | ship    | scooter     | bike      |

 